Grammar

    0 $accept: program $end

    1 program: PROGRAM IDENTIFIER SEMICOLON declarations_opt routine_list compound_statement DOT

    2 declarations_opt: ε
    3                 | VAR var_declaration_list

    4 var_declaration_list: identifier_list COLON type_specifier SEMICOLON
    5                     | var_declaration_list identifier_list COLON type_specifier SEMICOLON

    6 identifier_list: IDENTIFIER
    7                | identifier_list COMMA IDENTIFIER

    8 type_specifier: INTEGER_TYPE
    9               | BOOLEAN_TYPE

   10 routine_list: ε
   11             | routine_list routine

   12 routine: FUNCTION IDENTIFIER LPAREN parameters_opt RPAREN COLON type_specifier SEMICOLON declarations_opt compound_statement SEMICOLON
   13        | PROCEDURE IDENTIFIER LPAREN parameters_opt RPAREN SEMICOLON declarations_opt compound_statement SEMICOLON

   14 parameters_opt: ε
   15               | parameters

   16 parameters: parameter_group
   17           | parameters SEMICOLON parameter_group

   18 parameter_group: identifier_list COLON type_specifier

   19 compound_statement: BEGIN_TOKEN statement_list_opt END_TOKEN

   20 statement_list_opt: ε
   21                   | statement_list
   22                   | statement_list SEMICOLON

   23 statement_list: statement
   24               | statement_list SEMICOLON statement

   25 statement: compound_statement
   26          | IDENTIFIER ASSIGN expression
   27          | IF expression THEN statement
   28          | IF expression THEN statement ELSE statement
   29          | WHILE expression DO statement
   30          | FOR IDENTIFIER ASSIGN expression TO expression DO statement
   31          | WRITE LPAREN arguments_opt RPAREN
   32          | WRITELN LPAREN arguments_opt RPAREN
   33          | IDENTIFIER LPAREN arguments_opt RPAREN
   34          | RETURN_TOKEN expression

   35 arguments_opt: ε
   36              | argument_list

   37 argument_list: expression
   38              | argument_list COMMA expression

   39 expression: INTEGER_LITERAL
   40           | TRUE_TOKEN
   41           | FALSE_TOKEN
   42           | STRING_LITERAL
   43           | IDENTIFIER
   44           | IDENTIFIER LPAREN arguments_opt RPAREN
   45           | PARAM LPAREN expression RPAREN
   46           | LPAREN expression RPAREN
   47           | MINUS expression
   48           | NOT expression
   49           | expression PLUS expression
   50           | expression MINUS expression
   51           | expression STAR expression
   52           | expression SLASH expression
   53           | expression MOD expression
   54           | expression AND expression
   55           | expression OR expression
   56           | expression EQUAL expression
   57           | expression NOT_EQUAL expression
   58           | expression LT expression
   59           | expression LTE expression
   60           | expression GT expression
   61           | expression GTE expression


